title: Bug 134488: Set page break for table inside list group header will cause data display error.
OB: When setting a page break for a table inside a list group header, a data display error occurs.
SR:
To reproduce the issue: 
1. Insert a list with a group. 
2. Insert a table inside the list group header. 
3. Set the page break before the table to always. 
4. Preview in the web viewer or export to HTML/PDF.
